Description: Levi Global Empire was created in response to a void that traditional forms of marketing have created.
Headquarters Regions: Greater Detroit Area, Great Lakes, Midwestern US
Full Description: Founded in 2012 and headquartered in Troy, Michigan, our company was created in response to a void that traditional forms of marketing have created in the way you acquire market share: the lack of in-person contact between our demanding clients and their customer base. Since our humble beginning, Levi Global Empire has grown into a premier and global leader in marketing, sales, and communications firm among many industries. We specialize in face to face sales, marketing, and new customer acquisitions. We are fortunate to represent some of the nation’s most reputable companies in technology, telecommunications, cable & satellite as well as retail industries. Here at Levi Global Empire, we believe the best way to acquire a new customer for our clients is through face to face contact solidified by a smile and a handshake. By focusing our efforts on a one-on-one, relationship-based marketing, and sales approach, we are able to attach a face to a well-recognized client brand which in return allows us to increase customer and brand loyalty. The power of a live representative is unparalleled; the ability to inform the customer about industry changes, educate on our clients’ services and answer questions, as well as gaining their business.
